- [ ] "Hey Steve," prefix used
- [ ] Clear action description provided
- [ ] Rule compliance explicitly stated
- [ ] Purpose and method explained

#### Forbidden Actions
❌ Tool calls without "Hey Steve," prefix  
❌ Actions without rule reference  
❌ Unclear or vague action descriptions  
❌ Missing purpose or rationale  

### Success Criteria
- 100% "Hey Steve," prefix compliance
- Clear rule traceability for all actions
- Transparent decision-making process
- Enhanced user confidence in rule adherence

